nodes.text: This terrorist group was active in Lamaredd in 29 BBY. They were non-Humans with anti-Human ideology, and intended to take revenge on the crimes performed by tycoon Hugo Bartyn, who had settled Lamaredd five centuries before that moment.
In 29 BBY, the Jedi Council sent agents to Lamaredd to investigate the origin of the settlement. They discovered, among other things, this terrorist group.
